'''Lohema''' was a small [[Mining/Legends|mining]] town that was located on the [[Twi'lek/Legends|Twi'lek]] homeworld of [[Ryloth/Legends|Ryloth]]. The community became prosperous while digging for [[Ryll/Legends|ryll]] and precious metals. The mining operations were run by the [[Rooshan]] clan, who consequently became the leaders of the settlement. They enforced a strong work ethic among the miners and inflated their prices. [[Emen Rooshan]], one of the greediest of the Rooshan clan, grew so resentful of the nearby city of [[Joreikna]] that he hired assassins to kill some of the ruling clan of that city, the [[Ku'rys]].

